SVM¶

, , ..

( $\boldsymbol{x}^{T}\boldsymbol{w}-w_0=0$ ($\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{w}\in\mathbb{R}^p; w_0\in\mathbb{R}$).

: $$f\left(\boldsymbol{x}_i\right)=sign\left(\langle\boldsymbol{x}_i,\boldsymbol{w}\rangle -w_0\right),$$ $\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{w}\in\mathbb{R}^p; w_0\in\mathbb{R}$.

, $M_i=-\langle (\boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i),\boldsymbol{x}_i\rangle y_i$: $$L(M_i)=\max\{0,1+M_i\}$$

: $$ (\boldsymbol{x}^{T}\boldsymbol{w}-w_0) y_i > 0 $$ , $f\left(x\right)=sign{\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{T}\boldsymbol{w}-w_0\right)}$

, . (margin), : .

$\boldsymbol{w}$ : $$ \begin{cases} \boldsymbol{x}^{T}\boldsymbol{w}-w_0 = -1 \\ \boldsymbol{x}^{T}\boldsymbol{w}-w_0 = 1 \\ \end{cases} $$

$$ \begin{cases} \frac{1}{2}\langle\boldsymbol{w},\boldsymbol{w}\rangle\rightarrow \min\limits_{\boldsymbol{w} }\\ \left(\langle\boldsymbol{x}_i,\boldsymbol{w}\rangle - w_0\right)y_i \geq 1 \\ \end{cases} $$

:

--, : $$ \alpha_i \left[1-y_i\left(\langle\boldsymbol{x}_i,\boldsymbol{w}\rangle - w_0\right)\right] = 0\, \forall i$$

  1. $\alpha_i=0$ .. $\boldsymbol{w},w_0$
  2. $\alpha_i>0 \Rightarrow y_i \left(\langle\boldsymbol{x}_i,\boldsymbol{w}\rangle - w_0\right) = 1$ --

, $\left(\langle\boldsymbol{x}_i,\boldsymbol{w}\rangle - w_0\right)y_i \geq 1$ $i$. $\xi \geq 0$ : $$ \begin{cases} \frac{1}{2}\langle\boldsymbol{w},\boldsymbol{w}\rangle+C\sum\limits_{i=1}^n\xi_i\rightarrow \min\limits_{\boldsymbol{w},w_0 }\\ \left(\langle\boldsymbol{x}_i,\boldsymbol{w}\rangle - w_0\right)y_i \geq 1 -\xi_i\\, \end{cases}$$ C .

SVM :

$\phi (\boldsymbol{x}_i)$ - . , SVM , : $$ \boldsymbol{x}_i \rightarrow \phi (\boldsymbol{x}), ~ \boldsymbol{w} \rightarrow \phi (\boldsymbol{w}), ~ \langle \boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i \rangle \rightarrow \langle \phi (\boldsymbol{w}), \phi (\boldsymbol{x}_i) \rangle$$

- : $$K(\boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i) = \langle \phi (\boldsymbol{w}), \phi (\boldsymbol{x}_i) \rangle$$ $K$ -

: $$K(\boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i) = \langle \boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i \rangle$$

: $$K(\boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i) = (\langle \boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i \rangle + r)^d$$

: $$K(\boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i) = exp(-\gamma ||(\boldsymbol{w}-\boldsymbol{x}_i)||^2)$$

: $$K(\boldsymbol{w}, \boldsymbol{x}_i) = tahn(\gamma x^Ty+c_0)$$

Neural Nets¶

$X$ --- , $Y$ --- . $X^n = (x_i, y_i)_{i=1}^{n},$ $x_i \in \mathbb{R}^p$. $(x^1,\ldots,x^p)\in \mathbb{R}^p$ --- $x\in X$. : \begin{equation*} Q(a, X^n) = \frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^{n} \mathcal{L}(a,x_i,y_i) \rightarrow \min_w, \end{equation*} $a$ ( ): \begin{equation*} a(x, w) = \sigma( \langle w,x \rangle ) = \sigma\left(\sum_{j=1}^{p} w_j x^j - w_0 \right), \end{equation*} $w_k \in \mathbb{R}$, $k=0,\ldots,p$ --- ; $\sigma: \mathbb{R} \rightarrow \mathbb{R} $ --- ; $\mathcal{L}(a,x_i,y_i)$ --- , $i=1,\ldots,n$.
. $Y=\{+1,-1\}$. $\sigma (z)=sign (z)$, $a(x,w)$ --- , :
\begin{equation*} Q(w, X^{n})=\sum_{j=1}^{n} \mathcal{L} \left( a(x_j ,w), y_j \right) = \sum_{j=1}^{n} [y_j \langle w,x_j \rangle < 0] \rightarrow \min_{w}. \end{equation*}

: : $\sigma(z) = \frac{1}{1+e^{-a\,z}}$, $a \in \mathbb{R}$; Softmax: $SM_i(z) = \frac{e^{z_i}}{\sum_{k=1}^{K}e^{z_k}}$;

: $\sigma(z) = \frac{e^{a\,z} - e^{-a\,z}}{e^{a\,z} + e^{-a\,z}}$, $a \in \mathbb{R}$;

: $ReLU(p) = \max (0,p)$;
